This is the client part of the machine features repository. It can be used as abstraction layer by VOs to gather machine/job features no matter on which service flavor the payload is executed. 

src: the source code + setup.py script to produce a python module

test: test suite (unit test) and toy features mimicking bare metal file system deployment which are used by the tests

sam: the IT/Nagios SAM probe for testing machine/job features on WLCG infrastructures
